WEBVTT

27:37.772 --> 27:40.522
They cut a hole in the CF
dome using an atomic plasma torch.

27:41.313 --> 27:43.313
From the footprints, I'd
say there's eight to ten of them.

27:43.563 --> 27:43.772
Human.

27:44.397 --> 27:45.897
They rolled in on a remote armored snow

27:45.897 --> 27:47.980
cat, which they used
as a diversion before they

27:47.980 --> 27:50.188
blasted out of here
in a NORAD blind cargo jet.

27:50.355 --> 27:51.313
Good God, Cal.

27:51.897 --> 27:52.730
I'm going to find them, Zoe.

27:53.647 --> 27:54.855
We're going to work together on this.

27:56.188 --> 27:57.605
We were just told that someone hacked the

27:57.605 --> 27:59.563
Intercontinental
Seismic Surveillance System.

28:00.063 --> 28:01.897
I don't know if
it's related, but if someone

28:01.897 --> 28:03.647
knew where to look,
that's the only vulnerability

28:03.772 --> 28:04.355
in the cloaking.

28:05.272 --> 28:05.522
Who?

28:06.397 --> 28:06.980
We don't know yet.

28:07.272 --> 28:08.397
The trolls are scouring the web.
